SELWYN: So, Inspector,

56:26.280 --> 56:30.480
I just found this pack of cards

56:26.280 --> 56:30.480
by the backgammon set.

56:30.560 --> 56:32.000
Oh, gosh.

56:32.120 --> 56:37.120
Mary, do you think we should ask your nephew to perform

56:37.520 --> 56:40.720
one of his famous magic tricks, hmm?

56:40.920 --> 56:42.400
Oh, absolutely, Selwyn.

56:42.440 --> 56:45.240
No, look, really. Gosh,

56:42.440 --> 56:45.240
I mean, it's been so long.

56:45.280 --> 56:48.160
-I just don't... -Come on, Humphrey.

56:48.200 --> 56:49.760
Come on, chief.

56:50.320 --> 56:53.760
All right, then, JP, pick a card, any card.

56:54.000 --> 56:55.240
Okay.

56:55.880 --> 56:57.560
Now, don't let me see it.

56:57.600 --> 57:01.200
Show it to your friends and then place it

56:57.600 --> 57:01.200
back in the pack.

57:03.360 --> 57:04.520
Don't let me see it.

57:05.360 --> 57:08.240
Now, I can't possibly know what your card is.

57:08.280 --> 57:09.920
And by shuffling this pack,

57:09.960 --> 57:12.920
I can't possibly know where your card is.

57:14.240 --> 57:15.480
But...

57:16.120 --> 57:19.160
Tell me, did you choose a red card?

57:19.640 --> 57:20.640
JP: Yes.

57:21.240 --> 57:22.640
HUMPHREY: Was it a diamond?

57:25.480 --> 57:27.800
-Yes, sir.

57:28.480 --> 57:30.240
And that's exactly what I expected you to say,

57:30.280 --> 57:32.640
because the card you chose was the two of hearts.

57:34.480 --> 57:35.720
Ah, um, sorry.

57:35.880 --> 57:37.160
It's been a while.

57:37.200 --> 57:39.680
Ladies and gentlemen, the two of hearts.

57:42.840 --> 57:44.960
Right, bear with me. Wait, wait, here we go.

57:45.000 --> 57:46.560
Two of hearts.

57:47.640 --> 57:49.800
It was, um, queen of hearts.

57:49.840 --> 57:52.320
Two of hearts. Oh!

57:53.640 --> 57:56.600
It's got to be here somewhere. Wait,

57:53.640 --> 57:56.600
wait one second, it's coming.

57:56.640 --> 57:57.920
Two of hearts.

57:57.960 --> 57:59.880
The two of hearts.

58:00.880 --> 58:04.400
Catherine, there isn't even a two of hearts in this pack.

58:09.600 --> 58:11.760
ANOUK: Welcome to Le Calmar, Saint-Marie.

58:11.800 --> 58:14.200
Let the food do the talking.

58:14.320 --> 58:15.600
In here!

58:16.120 --> 58:19.080
Definitely attacked from behind,

58:16.120 --> 58:19.080
turned round and then...

58:20.880 --> 58:22.440
Hey! You little...

